FOX Africa recently treated media partners and invited guests to a night of jazzy rhythms and a delectable three course meal at Caramel Lounge and Restaurant in Westlands, Nairobi. The event marked the launch of FOX Life, an innovative new addition to the FOX Network Group into the African market.Hosted by tv presenter Sheila Mwanyigha, in attendance were DStv head of media sales Jackee Nyaga, FOX Africa Group sales and marketing director Baleseng Dlamini. Songbird June Gachui set a relaxed mood with her astounding performance.